    - language: 0
      text: Deal 10% more damage
    - language: 1
      text: "G\xE2y th\xEAm 10% s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng"
  - id: ste_0023_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Reflect 15% dmg taken
    - language: 1
      text: "Ph\u1EA3n l\u1EA1i 15% s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng nh\u1EADn v\xE0o"
  - id: ste_0024_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Deal +30% damage but take 15% hp damage for each action (HP cannot go
        down to 0 by this effect)
    - language: 1
      text: "G\xE2y th\xEAm 30% s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng nh\u01B0ng nh\u1EADn 15%
        HP hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i sau m\u1ED7i h\xE0nh \u0111\u1ED9ng (HP kh\xF4ng th\u1EC3
        xu\u1ED1ng 0 v\u1EDBi hi\u1EC7u \u1EE9ng n\xE0y)"
